<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Introduction - Data Privacy Hub</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background: #f9fafb;
        color: #121213;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    header {
        background-color: rgb(245, 228, 245);
        padding: 1rem 0;
        color: #333;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 100;
    }
    .navbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
    }
    .nav-logo {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #333;
    }
    .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links li {
        margin-left: 2rem;
    }
    .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #333;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover {
        color: #6c63ff;
    }
    :root {
      --primary: #6c63ff;
      --secondary: #4fd1c5;
      --dark: #2d3748;
      --light: #f7fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      padding: 5rem 0;
    }
    
    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .key-points {
        margin: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .key-points ul {
        list-style: none;
    }
    
    .key-points li {
        background: var(--white);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 3rem;
    }
    
    .key-points li:before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 1rem;
        top: 1.8rem;
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--primary);
    }
    
    footer {
      background-color: var(--dark);
      color: var(--light);
      padding: 3rem 0 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .footer-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
    
    .footer-section {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 250px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .footer-section h3 {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .footer-section ul {
      list-style: none;
    }
    
    .footer-section ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .footer-section ul li a {
      color: var(--light);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .footer-section ul li a:hover {
      color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    .copyright {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
      
      .content-section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .key-points li {
        padding: 1rem;
        padding-left: 2.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Data Privacy Hub</a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/introduction">Introduction</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guidance">Guidance</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy-laws">Privacy Laws</a></li>
        <li><a href="/gdpr">GDPR</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Introduction to Data Privacy</h2>
      
      <div class="key-points">
        <ul>
          <li>In the 21st century, data privacy stands as a critical pillar of digital trust, decisively shaping how personal information is collected, processed, and secured (Kuye, 2023).</li>
          <li>With the explosive growth of data-driven technologies—ranging from social media to artificial intelligence—individuals and organizations are confronted with significant challenges in safeguarding sensitive data (Liu, 2018).</li>
          <li>According to Torre, Alferez, Soltana, Sabetzadeh, & Briand (2020), global regulatory frameworks like the GDPR and New Zealand's Privacy Act 2020 aim to harmonize innovation with ethical data practices.</li>
          <li>This project investigates the technical, legal, and strategic dimensions of data privacy to provide actionable solutions for stakeholders.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-section">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/introduction">Introduction</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guidance">Guidance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy-laws">Privacy Laws</a></li>
          <li><a href="/rights">Your Rights</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h3>Resources</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Privacy Tips</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Compliance Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer-section">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="mailto:info@dataprivacyhub.nz">info@dataprivacyhub.nz</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Terms of Service</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="copyright">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Data Privacy Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>